Information we collect via cookies (which are small text files placed on your device).
Cookies allow us to collect data, such as your device's model, operating system and screen size and other information about how you use our Services.
For more information, please see  Our Use of Cookies and Related Technologies  Section of this Privacy Policy.
Information we collect via the use of pixel tags in marketing emails that we send to you (where we have your consent to do so) to measure open, click through and read rates and allow us to improve our emails.

Information we collect via the use of tracking links in marketing emails that we send to you (where we have your consent to do so) to measure click through and install rates to be able to evaluate how many users have downloaded the app.

